// Daulatabad Fort One of the most commanding and undefeatable forts in the entire country, Daulatabad Fort in Daulatabad; or Devagiri as it was known earlier, is among the must-visit places near Aurangabad. Around 11 km north-west of Aurangabad, this glorious fortress stands strong on a conical hill that stands around 200 m above the sea level.Looking back into the history of the fort, you will realize its importance and strength. Compared to the other forts within or far from the region, the defense of Daulatabad Fort was very strong. MH SH 22, Daulatabad, Maharashtra 431002 8 AM to 6 PM Aurangabad is the nearest city to reach Daulatabad Fort. Aurangabad is well connected by roadways from major cities of Maharashtra and direct state transport buses are available from cities like Mumbai, Pune, Nashik to reach Aurangabad.Further from Aurangabad, there are regular bus services to reach Daulatabad Fort. Tourists can also hire a private cab to reach the Devgiri fort. It is just a half-hour drive from Aurangabad to Dulatabad Fort.
